data.title: Rip Curl Dominates 2016 USA Surfing Championships
data.description:
Rip Curl's top junior surfers left their mark at the prestigious USA Surfing Championship at Lower Trestles, Ca. The team took home 3 Championship Titles, 2 runner-ups, and a 4th place finish. Rip Curl couldn't be more proud of this squad for all their efforts and achievements. Congrats team!

Starring: 
- Diego Ferri | U12 Runner-Up
- Alyssa Spencer | U14 2nd & U16 4th Place
- Robbie Goodwin | U12 Champion
- Brisa Hennessy | U18 Champion
- Crosby Colapinto | U16 Champion

Video/Edit: Justin Jung

data.title: The Lengths We Go To | Flashbomb E5 Flash Lining
data.description:
Rip Curl's new and exclusive E5 Flash Lining with 25% more stretch, faster drying time and a lighter lower profile.

Paired with slimline liquid tape technology and E5 stress point taping for the ultimate in sealed seams, this is the best cold water wetsuit ever made.

Music: Conway Hambone
Track: Cuban Stomp
Source: Getty Images

data.title: Dog Riding Wave - 2009 Dog Surfing Contest - Helen Woodward Animal Shelter
data.description:
Photos and Video Footage from the 2009 Helen Woodward Surf Dog Contest

Check out a quick clip from the 2009 Helen Woodward Dog Surfing Contest Event featuring surfing dogs from all over San Diego and Orange County. These dogs have a lot of courage and surf to raise money for homeless pets and animals.
